Package: QUEST
Title: Quantifying Uncertainty for Spatial Domain Detection in Spatial Transcriptomics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yanlin", "Tong", email = "zoetong@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: QUEST is a computational method for quantifying uncertainty in spatial domain detection using fuzzy clustering. It provides probabilistic domain assignments and location-level uncertainty estimates, enabling refinement of domain detection, identification of ambiguous regions such as domain boundaries and heterogeneous subdomains, and improvement of downstream analyses by focusing on high-confidence locations.
